reviewText: I rated this video with 4 stars.  I admit, I am a little biased.  I know Jewel so it's definitely a must have.  Actress/Author Jewel Shepard acts as your tour guide for a number of different sexy exercise routines and  vignettes to enhance your exercise routine.  Jewel is not the one doing the  exercising but she looks as gorgeous as ever.  You may not work up a sweat  watching this video, unless you watch it with a loved one, but you will  enjoy yourself.
